lead_paragraph: Honolulu-based Haru Nomura of Japan won her first LPGA tournament in her 72nd start, shooting a closing 7-under 65 on Sunday to win the Women's Australian Open by three strokes.

headline.print_headline: Japan's Nomura Wins Women's Australian Open by 3 Strokes
